                        <div class="bubble">
                            <span class="newsimg"><img src="../images/media/news/news161216.gif" alt=""/></span>
                            <p>We are pleased to note that China Mobile Limited was voted by analysts and investors as &quot;Best Managed Large Cap in China&quot; in &quot;Best Managed Companies Poll 2016&quot; organized by Asiamoney, and had won &quot;The Asset Platinum Award&quot; for Excellence in Governance, CSR and Investor Relations presented by Asset. These awards indicate the professional institutions&#39; and capital market participants&#39; recognition of the Company&#39;s good management, corporate governance, operations, strong execution, transparency and commitment in shareholder return and investor relations.<br><br>
							Headquartered in London, AsiaMoney is one of the leading financial magazines with international influence. It organizes polls and invites analysts and investors to vote for the best managed companies in Asia, and present the award to the first placed company in each of the small, medium and large capitalization categories. <br/><br/>
							The Asset is an influential regional financial magazine in Asia, it has organized the corporate awards for almost 20 years and recognizes the excellence of the listed companies in Asia through professional benchmarking and analysts interviews.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bubbleTail"></div>
                        <div class="bubbleDate">16 Dec 2016</div>
                   </div>
                </div>
				
